PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 36 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in SASKATCHEWAN in the spring of 1999 which caused extensive damage to agricultural lands, public works and private property, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 36 -
which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in SASKATCHEWAN in the spring of
1999 which caused extensive damage to agricultural lands, public works and
private property, to be of concern to the federal government, and
(b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
